text: Panakhes () is a rural locality (an aul) in Afipsipskoye Rural Settlement of Takhtamukaysky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 1594 as of 2018. There are 35 streets. == Geography == The aul is located 3 km west from Afipsip. == Ethnicity == The aul is inhabited by Circassians. == References == Category:Rural localities in Takhtamukaysky District
title: Panakhes
